Three disparate lives, three defining moments in time, one infinite loop. Epanalepsis, a cyberpunk-inspired tale, is now available on Steam for PC, Mac and Linux. 

From Cameron Kunzelman and Mastertronic comes Epanalepsis, a narrative-focused point-and-click adventure about life and technology. To the immersive sounds by music artist audiosprite, unravel the tangled threads of time and explore a curious story of connections across sixty years of urban life, paying homage to New Wave science-fiction, cyberpunk and 1990s art cinema. 

If you knew what your future holds, what would you change?  

